title: BRIEF-Cybercom inks framework agreement with Com Hem
text:
BRIEF-Cybercom inks framework agreement with Com Hem Sept 9 
Sept 9 Cybercom Group AB 
* Says Com Hem has signed framework agreement 
* Says the first task will be to take over responsibility for Com Hem's digital collaboration platform Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Stockholm Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
